<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_a8bd8907-4e1f-4985-b76a-a94fbdd06a62" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>C3P7</sptc><title id="_49b1c192-f511-4e2d-acfb-6fc46ae591ea">Access for maintenance</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_966a1ced-9f71-4949-babe-714cd5a24449" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_cb37b42f-539e-419d-b41b-f4095ad8e2b9">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1383_4.5.0.xml#_2396187d-8435-4f01-9dfd-613970a74823" id="_9fd106e9-17b8-44e7-a1e7-adf57191db47" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">On-site wastewater management systems</xref> that facilitate on-site storage, treatment, disposal or re-use of wastewater must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_ad6e644b-eeca-4f63-9578-6289a601b470">provide vehicle access for collection, if necessary; and</li><li id="_1393e8ef-3a16-4bec-b8e0-cce5d104f692">avoid the likelihood of unauthorised access by people; and</li><li id="_79b06940-7e11-4dd5-82ec-4209b5249677">permit cleaning, maintenance, measurement and performance sampling.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_472e4e60-702e-4501-b13c-7589a9989934" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_6fd999bc-961d-4125-ae6d-882a146dc0be">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Land application systems must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_add8e301-5728-49ad-865b-a6cda0d02dfc">provide access, as required, for maintenance; and </li><li id="_74aaf565-d61e-4882-9511-760749e3daa1">incorporate provisions, as required, for effective cleaning.</li></ol></subclause></clause>